OL,3,CCyclist, 11, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cbus while crossing road, says coroner
OL,6,FAn 11-year-old cyclist died after he
OL,7,Fwas struck by a bus and car in Derby,
OL,8,Fwhen it was not safe for him to cross
OL,9,Fthe road, a coroner has concluded.
OL,11,FSeth Fulton was riding on the pavement
OL,12,Falong Nottingham Road in Chaddesden on
OL,13,FApril 17th, when he saw his mother on
OL,14,Fthe other side of the road and decided
OL,15,Fto cross over to her.
OL,17,FHe was hit by a bus, which threw him
OL,18,Finto the path of a VW Polo, and he
OL,19,Fdied from his injuries the same day at
OL,20,Fthe Queen's Medical Centre in
OL,21,FNottingham.
