OL,3,CCyclist, 11, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cbus while crossing road, says coroner
OL,6,FSusan Evans, coroner for Derby and
OL,7,FDerbyshire, completed an inquest in
OL,8,Fwriting on Wednesday and concluded
OL,9,Fthat it was "not safe" for Seth to
OL,10,Fcross the road.
OL,12,FShe added that neither the driver of
OL,13,Fthe VW Polo nor the bus had
OL,14,F"sufficient opportunity" to avoid the
OL,15,Fcrash.
OL,17,FMs Evans concluded that Seth died in a
OL,18,Froad traffic collision, while his
OL,19,Fcause of death was recorded as a
OL,20,Ftraumatic head injury.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@VO]vD@AOUvD@XO]
