OL,3,CCyclist, 11, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cbus while crossing road, says coroner
OL,6,FThe coroner wrote on the record of
OL,7,Finquest: "On the 17th of April 2026,
OL,8,FSeth Fulton was cycling along the
OL,9,Fpavement of Nottingham Road in
OL,10,FChaddesden when he saw his mum on the
OL,11,Fopposite pavement.
OL,13,F"He attempted to cross the road when
OL,14,Fit was not safe to do so. He cycled in
OL,15,Ffront of a VW Polo car on the nearside
OL,16,Flane and as he got to the far side
OL,17,Fcarriageway, he was hit by a bus
OL,18,Fcoming from his left.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
