PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1784189889
OL,3,CCyclist, 11, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cbus while crossing road, says coroner
OL,6,F"This impact caused him to be thrown
OL,7,Finto the path of the VW Polo. He
OL,8,Fsuffered significant injuries and was
OL,9,Fconveyed to Queen's Medical Centre in
OL,10,FNottingham where he died later that
OL,11,Fday.
OL,13,F"Neither driver had sufficient
OL,14,Fopportunity to avoid a collision."
OL,16,FIn a statement released by Derbyshire
OL,17,FPolice after Seth's death, his parents
OL,18,Fsaid he "had a lust for life, loved
OL,19,Fwildlife and was adventurous".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@bO]zD@IOU{D@]O]
