OL,3,CCyclist, 11, died after being hit by
OL,4,Cbus while crossing road, says coroner
OL,6,FThey added: "Everyone who came into
OL,7,Fcontact with Seth will never forget
OL,8,Fhim. He loved his friends as much as
OL,9,Fthey all loved him."
OL,26,@nD@MOUqD@TO]
